	<head>
		
	<texsetting wysiwyg="0"/><paper pagenumber="1" margin="20,20,20,25">A4</paper></head>
	
<body fontsize="12pt" fontface="ＭＳ Ｐ明朝">
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">X</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">Y</munit></mblock>が相互に独立に<mblock><munit italic="1">N</munit><munit>(</munit><munit>0</munit><munit>,</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>に従う確率変数とする。このとき、<mblock><munit italic="1">U</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">X</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">Y</munit></mblock>の分布を表す確率密度関数を求めよう。</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit></mblock>の結合確率密度関数<mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>は</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">y<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p>である。</p>
<p/>
<p>今、</p>
<p/>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit></mblock></p>
<p/>
<p>とおく。これは</p>
<p/>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">y</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit></mblock></p>
<p/>
<p>と同じである。対応するヤコビアンは、</p>
<p/>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">J</munit><munit>=</munit><marray type="vert"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit>,</munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>1</munit></melem><melem><munit>0</munit><munit>,</munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit>1</munit></melem></marray><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mblock></p>
<p/>
<p>従って確率変数<mblock><munit italic="1">U</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">V</munit></mblock>の確率密度関数<mblock><munit italic="1">g</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>は、</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">g</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>{</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>)<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>}</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>{</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>)<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>}</munit></mlink></munit></mblock></p>
<p>となる。求めたいのは、<mblock><munit italic="1">V</munit></mblock>の値によって場合分けされていない、<mblock><munit italic="1">U</munit></mblock>の従う分布だから、<mblock><munit italic="1">V</munit></mblock>の取り得るあらゆる値に</p>
<p>ついて積分して、</p>
<p/>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">h</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink><mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit></mblock></p>
<p>が求める確率密度関数になる。<mblock><munit italic="1">e</munit></mblock>のべき指数は、</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">v<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>2</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></marray></mlink></munit><marray type="curly"><melem><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u</munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></marray><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>4</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit>1</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></marray></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u</munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></marray></mblock></p>
<p>それゆえ、</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">h</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></marray></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink><mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">infty</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></marray></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>)<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">v</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">e<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">u</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></marray></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">cdot</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" style="big">sqrt<mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray></mblock></p>
<p>このようにして、<mblock><munit italic="1">u</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>+</munit><munit italic="1">y</munit></mblock>は<mblock><munit italic="1">N</munit><munit>(</munit><munit>0</munit><munit>,</munit><munit>2</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>に従うことが分かる。</p>
<p/>
<p/>
